 Scripts for creating genetic maps:

Analyse_maps.R - main script for analysing the maps

comp_plot.R – Function for plot map comparison between consensus and framework maps

Compare_cluster_maps.R – Script to find LG correspondence between clusters, find split scaffolds and drop markers from LGs.

estimate_map_size.R - Resampling method to estimate map size and inflation

Find_order.R - ordering maps

Find_order.sh - shell script for running Find_order.R

first_part_of_BatchMap.R - Run initial steps of map creation

plot_recombinatio_maps.R - Plot results

segregation_test.R - test for segregation distortion 
